resources.string: This will recalculate your calories and nutrient goals which will overwrite any customer settings. Would you like to continue?

I understand that this will permanently delete my Restify account, that my information can't be recovered, and that this action can't be undone.

 I understand that I will permanently lose access to all of the data associated with my profile including food entries, workouts, steps entries, weight entries, notes, newsfeed posts, and photos.

 I understand that if I choose to rejoin Restify my username will not be available.
